org.odpi.openmetadata.frameworks.connectors.properties.beans.SearchKeyword
public class SearchKeyword extends ElementBase
SearchKeyword stores information about a keyword connected to an asset. SearchKeyword provide informal classifications to assets and can be added at any time - typically by the asset owner or curator.

      public String getName()
      Return the name of the keyword. It is not valid to have a keyword with no name. However, there is a point where the keyword object is created and the keyword name not yet set, so null is a possible response.
      Returns:
      String keyword name
